        "text": "<p>EVERYDAY CARE<br/>Enamel and mother of pearl are delicate materials that require special attention. Avoid impacts, friction, and contact with perfumes, cosmetics, or chemicals to preserve their surface and natural luster.<br/><br/>CLEANING AT HOME<br/>Clean using a soft, dry or slightly damp cloth, avoiding water immersion and any harsh or abrasive products. Do not use ultrasonic cleaners or steam, as they may damage these sensitive materials.<br/><br/>STORAGE<br/>Keep each piece separate in a soft pouch to prevent scratches and surface damage. Store away from heat, humidity, and direct sunlight to maintain their color and integrity over time.</p>",
